        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Cameras in the Courtroom Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Supreme Court to permit television coverage of all open sessions of the Court unless it decides by majority vote that allowing such coverage in a particular case would violate the due process rights of any of the parties involved.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
